data.description: Discover your own slice of paradise in this secluded Florida haven! Nestled on the desirable end lot of a tranquil cul-de-sac, this 3-bedroom, 2-bath cottage-style gem offers the utmost privacy with no neighbors behind or to one side, surrounded by lush greenery.    Step inside to find a home filled with seller upgrades, including a stunning leaded glass front door, chic laminate floors, and hurricane-impact windows throughout most of the residence. The dining room exudes elegance with wainscoting on the walls and ceiling, while the living room features a recessed ceiling adorned with crown molding.    The kitchen is a culinary delight, boasting cottage-style cabinets, Corian countertops, and a granite composite sink. Additional highlights include wainscoting on the kitchen ceiling and an updated backsplash. The spacious two-car garage, previously utilized as an art studio, comes complete with its own air conditioning unit while still maintaining its functionality as a garage.    The pièce de résistance is the expansive screened-in backyard oasis, a perfect retreat for relaxation or entertaining. Revel in the private outdoor space featuring a large heated swim spa and ample room for both guests and furry family members to unwind and enjoy.    Schedule a showing today to witness the charm and allure of this unique residence! Grand Palm, an exceptional community in Venice, Florida, offers resort-style living with a host of amenities. Residents can easily access downtown Venice and the beaches, just 20 minutes away. On-site activities, a state-of-the-art fitness facility, a resort-style pool with a water slide, and fitness pools for laps or water aerobics are just a few of the perks. Miles of walking and bicycle trails, Lookout Point Island, and dog parks cater to various interests, while sports enthusiasts can partake in basketball, tennis, bocce ball, pickleball, volleyball, and more. Live the dream at Grand Palm! (*Note: The crystal chandelier in the dining room is not included with the house.)
